PropertySetDef.Name: Pset_SystemFurnitureElementTypeSubrack
PropertySetDef.Definition: Properties of subrack used in railway telecom. The property set can be used by the predefined type SUBRACK of IfcSystemFurnitureElement

PropertyDef.Name: NumberOfSlots
PropertyDef.Definition: Indicates the number of device slots.

PropertyDef.Name: NumberOfUnits
PropertyDef.Definition: Indicates the number of vertical units.

PropertyDef.Name: NumberOfOccupiedUnits
PropertyDef.Definition: Indicates the number of vertical units occupied by the equipment.
